<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:14:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大众旗下 MAN 与 E.ON 合作开发电动卡车充电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/vws-man-eon-cooperate-electric-truck-charging-2024-07-11/</link><description>德国能源公司 E.ON 和大众汽车子公司 MAN Truck &amp;amp; Bus 周四公布了在德国和欧洲建立卡车充电网络的计划，以帮助减少排放并实现环境可持续的物流。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/vws-man-eon-cooperate-electric-truck-charging-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，随着美国降息押注的巩固，亚洲外汇空头有所缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-ease-us-rate-cut-bets-solidify-2024-07-11/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于对美联储今年至少两次降息的预期不断上升以及美元走软提振了风险情绪，大多数亚洲货币的空头头寸有所缓解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:38:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-ease-us-rate-cut-bets-solidify-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国全会交付的政策议程因目标相互冲突而受阻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plenum-deliver-policy-agenda-hindered-by-conflicting-goals-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国领导人将在下周举行的备受期待的会议上寻求为经济注入信心，但相互冲突的目标，例如在削减债务的同时促进增长，可能意味着在实施变革方面进展甚微。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plenum-deliver-policy-agenda-hindered-by-conflicting-goals-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>央行为何推出新的现金管理工具？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/why-does-chinas-central-bank-have-new-cash-management-tool-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国央行本周推出了一种新的现金管理工具，即临时债券回购协议和逆回购，增加了各种公开市场操作，并创造了可能成为重要利率指标的工具。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:04:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/why-does-chinas-central-bank-have-new-cash-management-tool-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>全球储备经理对经济增长持乐观态度，但担心政治</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-reserve-managers-upbeat-growth-worry-about-politics-2024-07-11/</link><description>周四发布的年度调查显示，央行储备经理普遍对世界经济前景持乐观态度，他们表示，地缘政治冲突升级是全球经济面临的最大风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-reserve-managers-upbeat-growth-worry-about-politics-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：IBAT在锂行业率先将新提取技术商业化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-industry-first-ibat-commercializes-new-extraction-technology-2024-07-11/</link><description>作为全球清洁能源转型的一个里程碑，国际电池金属公司成为第一家采用新型过滤技术商业化生产锂的公司，这一举措预计将带来更便宜、更快速的电动汽车电池金属供应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-industry-first-ibat-commercializes-new-extraction-technology-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国私营公司i-Space的火箭发射失败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/launch-rocket-chinese-private-firm-i-space-fails-2024-07-11/</link><description>官方新华社称，中国私营航天公司i-Space开发的双曲线一号火箭周四发射失败。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/launch-rocket-chinese-private-firm-i-space-fails-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>在美国通胀测试之前股市迈向历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-11/</link><description>亚洲股市周四上涨至历史新高，而英镑因强劲增长数据而小幅升至四个月高位，交易员们正在等待美国数据的公布，预计该数据将显示通胀放缓，并为最早在 9 月份降息铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国称北约关于其在俄罗斯-乌克兰冲突中的作用的声明是“恶意的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/planned-nato-statement-full-belligerent-rhetoric-lies-says-chinese-official-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国周四批评华盛顿北约峰会公报草案，该公报称其是俄罗斯在乌克兰发动战争的决定性推动者，是有偏见且“散布不和”的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/planned-nato-statement-full-belligerent-rhetoric-lies-says-chinese-official-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>台湾监视中国军事增兵，称中国对稳定构成威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-air-force-activity-after-carrier-passes-by-2024-07-11/</link><description>台湾周四表示，正在密切关注中国军队，称中国军队对该地区构成了越来越大的威胁，此前一系列战机经过台湾附近，参加与中国山东舰在太平洋的演习。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 01:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-air-force-activity-after-carrier-passes-by-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>英镑触及四个月高位，市场等待美国通胀数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-adrift-ahead-us-inflation-test-sterling-firms-2024-07-11/</link><description>英镑周四触及四个月高位，因英国央行政策制定者的言论和好于预期的GDP数据导致交易员减少了对8月降息的押注，同时等待重要的美国通胀数据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 01:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-adrift-ahead-us-inflation-test-sterling-firms-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>日本海军驱逐舰进入台湾附近中国海域，引发北京投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-navy-destroyer-enters-china-waters-near-taiwan-sparking-beijing-concerns-2024-07-11/</link><description>本月早些时候，一艘日本海军驱逐舰在没有通知中国的情况下罕见地进入台湾附近的中国领海，促使北京提出正式投诉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-navy-destroyer-enters-china-waters-near-taiwan-sparking-beijing-concerns-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体称多个澳门政府网站遭到黑客攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-macau-government-websites-hacked-says-chinese-state-media-2024-07-11/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三晚间报道，澳门多个政府网站遭到黑客攻击，警方已展开刑事调查，追查犯罪根源。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-macau-government-websites-hacked-says-chinese-state-media-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>北约峰会：华盛顿宣言的要点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/key-points-natos-washington-summit-declaration-2024-07-10/</link><description>北约国家领导人周三在华盛顿举行的峰会上发表声明，强调了对乌克兰的加入承诺，并对中国对俄罗斯的支持采取了更强硬的立场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/key-points-natos-washington-summit-declaration-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，特斯拉提高了欧洲 Model 3 的价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raises-model-3-prices-germany-due-european-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国汽车制造商特斯拉周三表示，在欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税后，特斯拉已将其在德国、荷兰和西班牙等欧洲国家的 Model 3 汽车价格提高约 1,500 欧元（1,622 美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raises-model-3-prices-germany-due-european-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>